Nu ka tae nya nyui wònye be amewo nava nyae be yewoate ŋu ado gbe ɖa na Yehowa ?
Ame geɖewo doa gbe ɖa le esi wònana woƒe dzi dzea eme ta , gake womexɔe se ŋutɔŋutɔ be Mawu ɖoa to gbedodoɖawo o .
Ehiã be woanya be Yehowa nye “ Gbedodoɖasela . ”
Hakpala David gblɔ be : “ Oo Gbedodoɖasela , gbɔwòe ame ƒomeviwo katã ava .
Yesu gblɔ na eƒe nusrɔ̃lawo be : “ Ne miebia nane le nye ŋkɔ me la , mawɔe . ”
