Maria Victoria : “ Meɖe kuku na Yehowa vevie be wòakpe ɖe ŋunye makpɔ nye aɖe dzi nyuie .
Medzudzɔ hadede kple ame siwo lɔ̃a amenyagbɔgblɔ hã .
Mexlẽ Psalmo 64 : 1 - 4 me nyawo , eye nyemedi kura be nɔviwo nanɔ gbe ɖom ɖa be [ Mawu ] nakpɔ yewo ta tso asinye me o !
Meva kpɔe hã be ne meyi edzi le ameŋunya gblɔm la , nyemanye kpɔɖeŋu nyui na amewo o , eye esia ahe vlododo ava Yehowa ƒe ŋkɔa dzi . ”
Linda : “ Mexlẽ míaƒe traktwo henya wo me nyawo nyuie be mate ŋu ama wo bɔbɔe .
Esi mede ha kple nɔvi siwo kpɔa gome le subɔsubɔdɔa ƒe akpa vovovowo me la , ekpe ɖe ŋunye ŋutɔ .
Eye mekpɔtɔ ɖoa ŋu ɖe Yehowa ŋu hedoa gbe ɖa nɛ . ”
